interpretation:
The Gibraltar flag represents the strength and resilience of a community that has overcome many challenges. It symbolizes unity, as the people of Gibraltar have come together to protect their heritage and defend their identity. This card reminds us that we have the power to overcome obstacles and achieve our goals if we work together and stay strong in the face of adversity.

The flag of Gibraltar is also a reminder of the importance of heritage and the value of preserving our cultural identity. It encourages us to connect with our roots and celebrate our traditions, as they are an essential part of who we are and where we come from.

In a tarot reading, the flag of Gibraltar may indicate a need for strength and perseverance in the face of challenges. It may also suggest a focus on heritage and cultural identity, or the importance of working together towards a common goal.
